CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

April 23, 2014

[Cite as 04/23/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-1674.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2013-2014. State ex rel. Howland v. Eckstein.

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lanzinger, French, and O’Neill, JJ., concur. O’Donnell and Kennedy, JJ., dissent and would grant an alternative writ.
